@startuml credential_session_start_sequence
' cc-tunnel セッション開始 + 再ログインフロー（セッションコンテナ統合方式・改訂版）

title Credential Session Start + Re-Login (Session Container Integration)

actor "User" as user
participant "Frontend" as fe
participant "cc-tunnel\nAPI Handler" as handler
participant "CredentialService" as credsvc
database "PostgreSQL\ncredentials" as db
participant "SessionManager" as sm
participant "Session Container\n(per conversationID)\ntmpfs:/home/user/.claude" as container

note over user, container
  改訂趣旨:
  - Cloud Run concurrency リスク回避のため cc-login 独立サービスを廃止
  - 認証も会話実行も同一の Docker セッションコンテナで実行
  - コンテナ単位の隔離が credentials のユーザー隔離を担保
end note

== /chat/:id 入室時 — CredentialGuard による status チェック ==

user -> fe : /chat/:id へアクセス
fe -> handler : GET /api/credentials/status\n(Bearer token)
handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)

alt credService == nil (no-auth mode)
  handler --> fe : 200 {registered: true, isValid: true}
else credentials 登録済み・有効
  credsvc -> db : SELECT WHERE username=$1
  db --> credsvc : row (is_valid=TRUE)
  credsvc --> handler : credentials_json
  handler --> fe : 200 {registered: true, isValid: true}
  fe -> fe : ChatPage を表示
else credentials 未登録 (ErrNotFound)
  credsvc --> handler : ErrNotFound
  handler --> fe : 200 {registered: false, isValid: false}
  fe -> user : navigate /login/credentials\n?reason=missing&conversationId=:id
else credentials 失効 (ErrCredentialsInvalid)
  credsvc --> handler : ErrCredentialsInvalid
  handler --> fe : 200 {registered: true, isValid: false}
  fe -> user : navigate /login/credentials\n?reason=expired&conversationId=:id
end

== Case A: credentials 既存・有効 ==

user -> fe : メッセージ送信
fe -> handler : POST /conversations/{id}/messages\n(Bearer token)
handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)
credsvc -> db : SELECT WHERE username=$1
db --> credsvc : row (is_valid=TRUE)
credsvc -> credsvc : AES-GCM Open(AAD=username)
credsvc --> handler : credentials_json
handler -> sm : GetOrCreate(conversationID, credentials_json)

alt 新規セッション
  sm -> container : ContainerCreate (tmpfs:/home/user/.claude) + Start
  sm -> container : POST /init {credentialsJson}
  container --> sm : 200 (credentials.json 書き込み完了)
end

handler -> container : POST /execute (会話実行)
container -> container : claude CLI 起動
container --> handler : NDJSON events
handler --> fe : 202 Accepted

== Case B: credentials 未登録（→ Case D へ誘導） ==

user -> fe : メッセージ送信
fe -> handler : POST /conversations/{id}/messages
handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)
credsvc -> db : SELECT WHERE username=$1
db --> credsvc : (no rows)
credsvc --> handler : ErrCredentialsNotFound
handler --> fe : 401 {error: "credentials_required",\n      redirect: "/login/credentials?reason=missing&\n                conversationId=..."}
fe -> user : 「認証情報が必要です」

== Case C: credentials 失効（→ Case D へ誘導） ==

user -> fe : メッセージ送信
fe -> handler : POST /conversations/{id}/messages
handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)
db --> credsvc : row (is_valid=FALSE)
credsvc --> handler : ErrCredentialsInvalid
handler --> fe : 401 {error: "credentials_invalid",\n      redirect: "/login/credentials?reason=expired&\n                conversationId=..."}

== Case D: 再ログインフロー（セッションコンテナ統合の核心） ==

user -> fe : 「ログイン」クリック
fe -> handler : POST /api/credentials/relogin/start\n{conversationId}
handler -> sm : GetOrCreate(conversationID, credentials=nil)
sm -> container : ContainerCreate (tmpfs 空) + Start
note right of container
  credentials なしで起動。
  /init は呼ばない。
end note
sm --> handler : ready
handler --> fe : 200 {ready: true}

fe -> handler : POST /auth/login\n（既存 endpoint）
handler -> container : remoteClient.InitiateLogin
container -> container : exec.Command("claude", "/auth")\n+ pty.Start()
container --> handler : PTY 起動完了
handler --> fe : 200 {message, loginUrl?}

loop ユーザー認証完了まで
  fe -> handler : GET /auth/pty/stream?conversationId=...\n(text/event-stream, SSE)
  handler -> container : remoteClient.SubscribePTYStream
  container --> handler : PTY stdout (SSE events)
  handler --> fe : SSE event stream
  fe -> user : ターミナル UI 出力 (xterm.js renderer)

  user -> fe : 入力（OAuth コード等）
  fe -> handler : POST /auth/input
  handler -> container : remoteClient.SubmitAuthInput
  container -> container : PTY stdin write
end

note over container
  claude CLI が OAuth 完了 →
  /home/user/.claude/.credentials.json
  をコンテナ内 tmpfs に書き込む
end note

container --> handler : "Login successful"

fe -> handler : POST /api/credentials/relogin/finalize\n{conversationId}
handler -> container : remoteClient.FinalizeCredentials\n(POST /auth/finalize-credentials)
container -> container : os.ReadFile(~/.claude/.credentials.json)
container --> handler : 200 {credentialsJson: "<生 JSON>"}
handler -> handler : Encryptor.Seal(json, AAD=username)\n→ ciphertext, nonce
handler -> db : UPSERT credentials\nON CONFLICT(username) DO UPDATE\n(encrypted_data, nonce, is_valid=TRUE, updated_at)
db --> handler : OK
handler --> fe : 200 {registered: true, isValid: true}

note right of container
  credentials.json は tmpfs 上に残るが、
  コンテナ破棄（会話終了 / アイドル停止）で
  自動消滅する。明示的削除は不要。
end note

fe -> user : 「認証完了」→ Case A に合流

== Case E: 実行中に Anthropic API 401（失効を実行時検出） ==

container -> container : claude CLI が API 401
container --> handler : event {error: 401}
handler -> credsvc : MarkInvalid(username)
credsvc -> db : UPDATE SET is_valid=FALSE
note right of fe
  次回送信時には Case C で
  redirect が返り、ユーザーは
  Case D へ誘導される
end note

@enduml
